      {
        "id": 284266,
        "name": "üëäüá∫üá∏üî•",
        "username": "Avitus",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/avitus/{size}/34172_2.png",
        "created_at": "2026-02-09T21:17:08.976Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal is already hardened: messages are end-to-end encrypted, registration lock to combat account takeover, Signal PIN to prevent impersonation in the event of account takeover, hide phone number in conversations, hide phone number from discoverability, and hardware encryption via OS lock screen password.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"desmond\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"74660\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/e495f1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> desmond:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Text only mode stripping down everything else. Just plain text messages. Signal Lite app?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>What would be the purpose of this?</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"desmond\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"74660\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/e495f1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> desmond:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Total block of unknown numbers and contacts or usernames. (pls!)</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>You can already hide your number from discoverability via settings &gt; privacy &gt; who can find me by phone number &gt; nobody.</p>\n<p>The likelihood of scammers guessing a username is very low. If there is an excessive spam problem to your username, you can change the username to stop it.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"desmond\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"74660\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/e495f1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> desmond:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>One click can switch on many other settings such as: disabling link previews, relay calls through signal servers only protecting IP, PIN, registration lock, incognito keyboard, turning off phone number visibility and discoverability, app lock, screen security,</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"desmond\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"74660\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/e495f1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> desmond:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PIN</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Users are already prompted to create a Signal PIN on account creation.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"desmond\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"74660\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/e495f1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> desmond:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>turning off phone number visibility and discoverability</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Users are already prompted to turn this on at onboarding.</p>\n<p>The rest of that list should be left to be toggled a la carte. One button for all of it would confuse less tech-savvy users.</p>",
