        "created_at": "2026-02-12T12:25:42.909Z",
        "cooked": "<p>As others have discussed here, I too would like to add that WhatsApp has recently introduced something called ‚ÄúStrict account settings‚Äù feature resembling this request.</p>\n<p>But besides that, I actually need to request here that as we grow old, we need to develop a robust and safe solution for the population not adopted to such advanced features. Basic functions must continue to work while keeping security and privacy within user reach.</p>\n<p>I feel if we could reduce whatever friction out there for them (and everyone too) than this can help achieve a really good goal in the long term.</p>",
